courses.EventName: SWIM - PARENT AND TOT 2 - GOLDFISH - (12-24 MONTHS) - PRESCHOOLERS
courses.Details: Learn how to enter and exit the water together; play games that encourage toddlers to blow bubbles in the water and get faces wet; and start to develop floating and kicking skills. Parent participation required. Pre-requisite: None.
